name: Karen Tamara Adams
description: I’m 33 years old single never been married before and no kids I’m from Syria, I left Syria because of the on going war crisis that has been rolling over few years now killing and burning of houses and properties, i left Syria to secure my life at a refugee Camp In Benin were other Refugee people are staying for safety, I missed the first barged in Turkey and Jordan the UNHCR brought us to Benin New Camp, I’m a nurse by profession.
